«Марина в огне» (Marina v Ogne)
================================

A browser-based lead-magnet text game about founder burnout.

This is a derivative work based on:

    "A Dark Room"
    Copyright (c) Michael Townsend / Doublespeak Games
    https://github.com/doublespeakgames/adarkroom
    Licensed under the Mozilla Public License, v. 2.0.

«Марина в огне» uses the A Dark Room engine (jQuery-based module loader,
state manager, notification system, button primitives) as a framework,
and implements a new minimal game loop about a founder's first days
building a content studio.

Modifications © 2026 Tim Zinin, released under the Mozilla Public License,
v. 2.0. See LICENSE.md for full text or visit https://mozilla.org/MPL/2.0/.

Source (including all modifications) is publicly available at:
    https://github.com/TimmyZinin/marina-v-ogne

Audio assets from the upstream A Dark Room repository have been
REMOVED from this fork to avoid distributing content with unclear
rights. «Марина в огне» ships silent.
